        <abstract> 
<p>Belated thanks to CL for copy of <hi rend="italic">Elements</hi>. Praises CL’s work. Notes especially Atlantic continents, the Weald, the Purbeck beds, glacial action, and the formation of lake-basins.</p> 
            <p>Also mentions account of Heer’s work</p>
            <p>and CD’s disagreement with J. D. Forbes.</p> 
<p>Suggests that CL have Murray print a two-volume edition [of the <hi rend="italic">Elements</hi>].</p> 
        </abstract>
